      "text": "In this experiment I provided a cursor's eye view of the live screen using a purpose built system that recorded mouse motion and then rendered frames in non-realtime. "
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "id": "bc3d8a3712228a9b",
      "text": "I was frustrated that Smalltalk in the '80s didn't have the horsepower to generate live video. I discovered it could bitblt smallish bitmaps at 15Hz. So I set out to generate interesting movies in this format."
    },
